-Hooks are a type of Method which are used to make Synchronization between the State And UI.
-Hooks make the UI updation easily.
-In the Given Example Code of Counter if We don't use Hooks then on Click the Counter Value is not Change in UI but it change in it's own.
-So, on changing the value of Variable the Hooks are Responsible to make change in UI where the variable is Used.

-React Control the UI Updation on a single click hence we tell it as a reactive library.

example of Hooks---
                1- useState()
                2- useEffect()
                3- useRef()
                4- useCallback()
                5- useNavigate()
                6- useHistory()
                etc...
